Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.34,0:00:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A magazine page I can't finish reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to read it, but somehow I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.08,0:00:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Game software is stacked in the corner of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.86,0:00:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't play them, will they become meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.79,0:00:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm just beyond the table, and I'm trying to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.61,0:00:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A never changing facial expression is on your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm right here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They can't reach, they can't reach, these feelings of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:01:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder what's really important?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.48,0:01:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\be1}My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.77,0:01:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HE94E0A&}Black Chaos{\c&HFFFFFF&}, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spell of Destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death Ultima!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.86,0:01:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand Eyes Sacrifice was beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.16,0:01:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YUGI WON!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ALRIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ALRIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The King of Duelists"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.04,0:02:00.12,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Pegasus go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:04.63,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Anzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:06.88,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.30,0:02:08.17,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.59,0:02:11.45,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,At the top of the tower, Pegasus' secret room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:16.68,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,But my memory's not clear and I thought I was dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.26,0:02:19.27,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:24.65,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't tell if it was real or a dream, so I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.85,0:02:26.02,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:29.15,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,Explain it clearly for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.15,0:02:31.94,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,It was real after all. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:35.37,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,Oi~ You still haven't told us everything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.70,0:02:47.92,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen many different types of minds using the Millennium Eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:53.55,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,But for there to be two minds in one body...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:56.84,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the Millennium Puzzle's power?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:18.70,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,Cyndia, I'm beginning to think I may have been wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.04,0:03:21.87,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:29.04,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,You're a user of the Power of Darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:32.67,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,So the Millennium Eye grants one the power to read people's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:36.44,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,But can you read {\i1}your future{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:42.97,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay put in this room a while and you'll learn {\i1}everything{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.73,0:03:47.10,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use these cards to help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.40,0:04:00.32,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,This card represents your birth and youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:08.21,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,Happy Lover? You seem to have gone through happy romance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.62,0:04:11.59,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,But this card is upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:16.09,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you and your lover suffered a tragic end.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:18.68,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like I guessed right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:22.22,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,The next card represents your current self.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:25.22,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,Mask of Darkness, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.60,0:04:31.02,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,Your current position and actions are to hide your {\i1}original{\i0} objectives, like a mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:33.83,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,In order to cover up the {\i1}true{\i0} objectives deep within your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.32,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,you cooked up {\i1}quite{\i0} the lengthy scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.50,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,-And those true objectives...\N -Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:46.80,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Oi~! I just drew an unlucky card!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:49.75,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel of Silencing Death, Doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:52.22,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to be an angel but it brings death.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.42,0:04:57.17,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,And once it appears before you, there's no escaping your passage to the underworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:12.33,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,Is this all the power the Millennium Eye can muster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.77,0:05:17.82,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of the Duel with Yugi boy, my mind has reached its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:25.49,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,Who {\i1}are{\i0} you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:31.87,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm collecting the seven Millennium Items.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:34.89,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:40.40,Default,Bakura,0000,0000,0000,,Once one gathers them all, you are granted a power strong enough to control the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.73,0:05:44.55,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,Stop... Stop it!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:48.41,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,NO~!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:05:58.44,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.07,0:06:03.20,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:06.53,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,Croquet-san, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:08.87,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Master Pegasus was attacked by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:13.29,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about Grandpa, Kaiba-kun and Mokuba-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.62,0:06:14.96,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,No's not the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:18.73,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,Just who did this to Pegasus...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's check out his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:23.63,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Maybe we could find some clues in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:28.01,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,That lady sure is pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:33.69,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,This is a diary... It's Pegasus' diary!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.81,0:06:34.40,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:35.56,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus' diary?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:38.27,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,It's in English!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:42.03,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Pegasus is an American!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:43.61,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,Can you read it, Anzu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:46.49,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,I can try reading it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:51.41,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,"To the one who defeats me and becomes the new Duelist King."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:55.08,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,"Why did I create Duel Monsters?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:07:00.46,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,"In order to explain this mystery, I must talk about this girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:05.30,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus must have wrote this just in case he lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:06.84,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey~ Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:09.39,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same girl as the portrait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:13.77,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,"Cyndia, that was the name of this young girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:18.59,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She was my lover and she passed away from this world at the age of seventeen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:23.69,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has been 14 years since I first met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.49,0:07:28.53,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My father was a wealthy man who managed casinos in Las Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.91,0:07:33.79,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In the evening, important people assembled for parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.21,0:07:38.58,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At that time I met Dad's friend's daughter, Cyndia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.59,0:07:49.93,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We were attracted to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:53.52,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have always talked about our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:56.31,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,I dreamed of becoming an artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.31,0:07:58.77,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Also to travel to many countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:08:02.82,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We swore the two of us would live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.25,0:08:24.05,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Soon after I turned 17, Cyndia died of an illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:33.39,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For months I stared at the blank canvas of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:41.19,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At that time, I had heard about how according to Ancient Egyptian belief, souls lived on after death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:47.21,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perhaps I could meet Cyndia if I used the technique handed down in Ancient Egypt...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:51.28,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I visited Egypt with that purpose in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:55.62,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In a certain village in Egypt, I met a young boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:03.54,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:05.48,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,You, stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:08.67,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give you some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:11.07,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this place at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.89,0:09:13.76,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,What you are looking for is not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:18.56,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,You won't heal your grief for your begone beloved in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.13,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.05,0:09:51.59,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,You ignored my warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:55.76,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.85,0:10:00.53,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the guardian of the Millennium Items.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:06.36,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to leave this sacred place is to be one of those chosen by the Millennium Items as their owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:10.61,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell anyone about this, so please let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.11,0:10:16.58,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,From this moment, you will be tested by this Millennium Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.66,0:10:20.62,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,Millennium... Eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:24.92,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,If it recognizes you as its owner,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.96,0:10:29.30,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,the Millennium Item will grant you one wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:30.30,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,Wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:36.14,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The doors of the underworld will open, and you will be able to see your lover again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:38.14,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,Cyndia...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.35,0:10:43.39,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,But if it doesn't recognize you as its owner, the only thing awaiting you is... {\i1}death{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:16.22,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,Cyndia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:24.89,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,Cyndia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:31.11,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see you, I wanted to see you, Cyndia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:36.07,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,Cyndia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.37,0:11:40.78,Default,Pegasus,0000,0000,0000,,Cyndia...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:46.51,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,"It might have been lingering affection, but I wanted to meet Cyndia once again."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:53.31,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,"At the time, I became aware of Kaiba Corporation's Virtual Simulation System."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.47,0:11:56.84,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,"In order to materialize Cyndia's card,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.88,0:11:59.97,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba Corporation had to be mine, no matter what it took."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.14,0:12:04.68,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus wanted to meet his dead lover from the bottom of his heart
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.27,0:12:07.90,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,and was willing to take over Kaiba Corporation for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.35,0:12:10.44,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,A man's true love?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:18.16,Default,Honda,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't care about Bakura and Mokuba, they'll be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.78,0:12:20.32,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,And Kaiba too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:21.03,Default,Anzu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:25.25,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,This card?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:28.21,Default,Jounouchi,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, what are you doing? Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:30.13,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.26,0:12:36.22,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:46.81,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:53.86,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It can't be. It's this young man who has the Millennium Puzzle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:58.20,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this kid the one who stole Pegasus' Millennium Eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:01.99,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I need to confirm this young man's true identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:03.33,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.62,0:13:10.12,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll use the Millennium Ankh to look at this young man's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:11.63,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.89,0:13:28.64,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.73,0:13:33.36,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are two rooms in this boy's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:38.03,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One has toys laid out all over the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.11,0:13:43.41,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doesn't look like the criminal who took the Millennium Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:45.83,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's another room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:56.80,Default,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think anyone would come to investigate my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.67,0:14:03.01,Default,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,If you're brave enough, come in. A game is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:10.56,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have looked into many humans' rooms in their hearts in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:17.90,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But this kind of serious and cold room is like the Ancient Egyptian grave of a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.28,0:14:22.66,Default,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what kind of powers you have used to come into my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:24.70,Default,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,State your purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:29.04,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,Answering your question is a common courtesy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:33.08,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,Since Egyptian times, for 3000 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:36.92,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,The royal families have handed down the Dark Millennium Items.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.25,0:14:41.67,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,The seven items have the ability to rule the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.97,0:14:45.72,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,And there are an infinite number of people collecting these items.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.05,0:14:50.35,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,I am the guardian of the Millennium Items.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.52,0:14:54.48,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I'm searching for the one who took Pegasus' Millennium Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:58.40,Default,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,And you think this criminal is me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:15:03.11,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,By looking at one's room, I can sense any power within.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:09.58,Default,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,I see. In this heart you've found my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.58,0:15:11.08,Default,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,The truth has been revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:15.17,Default,Yami,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a game. A Dark Game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:18.67,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,I shall accept this game.
