Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.54,0:16:00.84,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\i1}This door and this door aren't it. It's not the real room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:03.76,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just which one is the real door?
