Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:14.62,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:19.04,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,Counting from now, 3000 years ago in Ancient Egypt,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:23.38,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,There were stone tablets sealed under the control of magicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.38,0:17:27.26,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,The battle for the king's throne begins with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.51,0:17:34.43,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,Soon after the magicians were destroyed, the stone tablets and their magical powers went into sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:38.89,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,Those stone tablets' legends were all recorded in a history book.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.14,0:17:44.27,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,After it was around humans, it soon was made into cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:46.19,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,And it is the starting point of the card game.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:50.32,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,These stone tablets are Duel Monsters in its original state?
