Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.49,0:18:34.91,Default,Shadi,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.03,0:18:37.20,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1FA1BC&}Black Magician {\c&HFFFFFF&}is my card.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:42.87,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1FA1BC&}Black Magician{\c&HFFFFFF&}, we aren't here in this room to cause chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.17,0:18:45.33,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,Allow us to escape from this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:49.46,Default,Yugi,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1FA1BC&}Black Magician{\c&HFFFFFF&}!
